org.jhove2.module.format
Class BaseFormatModule

java.lang.Object
  org.jhove2.core.reportable.AbstractReportable
      org.jhove2.module.AbstractModule
          org.jhove2.module.format.BaseFormatModule
All Implemented Interfaces:
Reportable, FormatModule, Parser, Module
Direct Known Subclasses:
ArcModule, Bytestream, DirectoryModule, FileSetModule, GzipModule, ICCModule, SgmlModule, ShapefileModule, TiffModule, UTF8Module, WarcModule, WAVEModule, XmlModule, ZipModule
@Persistent
public class BaseFormatModule
extends AbstractModule
implements FormatModule

Base JHOVE2 format module. Modules for specific formats/format families will inherit from this module. Any single format module that inherits from this class can be invoked as a Command.

Author:
mstrong, slabrams, smorrissey
